## ⚙️ How to Run Locally

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/skyline180/EV-Dashboard-Streamlit.git
cd EV-Dashboard-Streamlit

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Launch the app
streamlit run streamlit_ev_dashboard.py
```
